    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and character-filled ride! This car is in fair condition, offering a solid foundation for someone who appreciates a vehicle with a bit of history. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its journeys, it remains a reliable choice for daily commuting or weekend errands. With a little bit of care, this car will continue to be a great companion on all your adventures!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a dedicated project car or a source for parts. While it currently starts, it suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a slipping transmission and noticeable engine oil leaks. The exterior has heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows substantial wear and tear with torn upholstery. It will require a trailer for transport and significant investment to return to a roadworthy state.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
